room_title: Escape room "Time Breaker Challenge" by BreakoutStudios in San Jose
room_description: Designed by Colonel Blaylock, this challenge is the first step for those who enlist in the TIME BREAKERS force. You are transported to the Colonel’s secret training location. There, you’ll face the tests created by some of the GREATEST MINDS OF SCIENCE. You are split into 2 groups, and have to collaborate, communicate and use your problem-solving skills to beat the challenge. Are you good enough to pass the challenge?
